articles.title: Australian Open 2023 badminton: HS Prannoy loses in final - Olympics
articles.description: Indian badminton player HS Prannoy lost to China’s Weng Hong Yang 9-21, 23-21, 20-22 in the Australian Open 2023 men’s singles final on Sunday. Get results, scores.
articles.content:
Indian badminton player HS Prannoy lost to the Peoples Republic of Chinas Weng Hong Yang 9-21, 23-21, 20-22 in the Australian Open 2023 mens singles final in Sydney on Sunday.
